---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Galerija">
  <Header />

  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex-grow">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-kk-primary">Galerija</h1>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
      <svg class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-4 text-kk-primary opacity-50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
      </svg>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">
        Galerija je u pripremi. Uskoro će biti dostupna sa preko 200 slika iz istorije našeg kluba.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        Fotografije sa utakmica, turnira i posebnih događaja biće organizovane po albumima za lakše pretraživanje.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
